he near future.&rdquo;</p>\n<p>To read the full article, please <a href=\"http://www.mwe.com/Treasury-Department-and-IRS-Release-Initial-Lifetime-Income-Guidance-Additional-Guidance-Expected-Shortly-02-24-20121/?PublicationTypes=d9093adb-e95d-4f19-819a-f0bb5170ab6d\">click here</a>.&nbsp;</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/MWE-EmployeeBenefitsBlog/~4/YvWK10Vd75A\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"http://feeds.lexblog.com/~r/MWE-EmployeeBenefitsBlog/~3/YvWK10Vd75A/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:176:\"http://www.employeebenefitsblog.com/2012/02/articles/retirement-plans/treasury-department-and-irs-release-initial-lifetime-income-guidance-additional-guidance-expected-shortly/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:8:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"DOL\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:6:\"domain\";s:40:\"http://www.employeebenefitsblog.com/tags\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"Defined Contribution Retirement Plans\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:6:\"domain\";s:40:\"http://www.employeebenefitsblog.com/tags\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"IRS\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:6:\"domain\";s:40:\"http://www.employeebenefitsblog.com/tags\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"Individual Retirement Accounts\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:6:\"domain\";s:40:\"http://www.employeebenefitsblog.com/tags\"