/73-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(75,1,'2012-04-20 13:28:12','2012-04-20 18:28:12','[question]What weekly classes do I take as a member of the Steps Dance Company?[/question]\r\n\r\n[answer]We value our company members earning a well rounded dance education. As a Steps Dance Company member you will be required to take two ballet classes per week, a jazz technique class, and another class of your choosing. Most company members are required to take a tap technique class as well.[/answer]','FAQ','','publish','open','open','','faq','','','2012-04-20 13:28:12','2012-04-20 18:28:12','',73,'http://steps.dev/?page_id=75',0,'page','',0),(76,1,'2012-04-20 13:27:34','2012-04-20 18:27:34','','FAQ','','inherit','open','open','','75-revision','','','2012-04-20 13:27:34','2012-04-20 18:27:34','',75,'http://steps.dev/75-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(77,1,'2012-04-20 13:28:47','2012-04-20 18:28:47','Placement into one of our Steps Dance Companies is by audition only.  Our company auditions will take place June 11-14, 2012.  Our auditions are divided by age group as well as style.  We have separate auditions for our hip-hop, tap, and ballet companies.','Auditions','','publish','open','open','','auditions','','','2012-04-20 13:28:47','2012-04-20 18:28:47','',73,'http://steps.dev/?page_id=77',1,'page','',0),(78,1,'2012-04-20 13:28:36','2012-04-20 18:28:36','','Auditions','','inherit','open','open','','77-revision','','','2012-04-20 13:28:36','2012-04-20 18:28:36','',77,'http://steps.dev/77-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(79,1,'2012-04-20 13:29:16','2012-04-20 18:29:16',' ','','','publish','open','open','','79','','','2012-04-20 13:29:16','2012-04-20 18:29:16','',0,'http://steps.dev/?p=79',11,'nav_menu_item','',0),(80,1,'2012-04-20 13:29:16','2012-04-20 18:29:16',' ','','','publish','open','open','','80','','','2012-04-20 13:29:16','2012-04-20 18:29:16','',73,'http://steps.dev/?p=80',13,'nav_menu_item','',0),(81,1,'2012-04-20 13:29:16','2012-04-20 18:29:16',' ','','','publish','open','